ax, which is what matters.\n\nLooking more carefully at the section titles, I notice the knowledge file has s2 labeled with the document's main title rather than the actual RST heading \"クラス図\" that appears in the source. That's a structural mismatch I should correct. I've reviewed the knowledge file structure and identified the core issue: s2's title is incorrectly set to the document title rather than \"クラス図\", which is the actual h2 heading in the RST source. Everything else appears to be in order.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14546,"cache_read_input_tokens":18561,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":14546,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e8043bf6-bc02-4cea-ade5-565abd1588fb","uuid":"ce19dff0-4371-4e66-91d6-094fbc0fa46d"}
